tooltip.ae2additions.quantum_unit.01=Interior filler block for Quantum Computers.
tooltip.ae2additions.quantum_unit.02=Provides no extra storage or parallelism.
tooltip.ae2additions.quantum_unit.03=Use it to fill the interior; air is not allowed inside.
tooltip.ae2additions.quantum_core.01=Required for Quantum Computers; install exactly 1.
tooltip.ae2additions.quantum_core.02=Provides 256M crafting storage and 8 parallel tasks.
tooltip.ae2additions.quantum_core.03=The interior may not contain air.
tooltip.ae2additions.quantum_storage_128.01=Adds 128M crafting storage to a Quantum Computer.
tooltip.ae2additions.quantum_storage_128.02=No quantity limit; place it inside the structure.
tooltip.ae2additions.quantum_storage_256.01=Adds 256M crafting storage to a Quantum Computer.
tooltip.ae2additions.quantum_storage_256.02=No quantity limit; place it inside the structure.
tooltip.ae2additions.data_entangler.01=Install at most 1.
tooltip.ae2additions.data_entangler.02=Multiplies total Quantum Computer storage by 4.
tooltip.ae2additions.quantum_accelerator.01=Adds 8 parallel tasks to a Quantum Computer.
tooltip.ae2additions.quantum_accelerator.02=No quantity limit; place it inside the structure.
tooltip.ae2additions.quantum_multi_threader.01=Install at most 1.
tooltip.ae2additions.quantum_multi_threader.02=Multiplies total Quantum Computer parallelism by 4.
tooltip.ae2additions.quantum_structure.01=Outer shell block for Quantum Computers.
tooltip.ae2additions.quantum_structure.02=Build a rectangular shell that is 1 block thick.
tooltip.ae2additions.quantum_structure.03=Default maximum outer size is 7x7x7.
tooltip.ae2additions.assembler_matrix_frame.01=Outer frame block for Assembler Matrices.
tooltip.ae2additions.assembler_matrix_frame.02=Build a rectangular frame that is 1 block thick.
tooltip.ae2additions.assembler_matrix_frame.03=Edges and corners must use frames.
tooltip.ae2additions.assembler_matrix_wall.01=Outer wall block for Assembler Matrices.
tooltip.ae2additions.assembler_matrix_wall.02=Fills each face of the frame.
tooltip.ae2additions.assembler_matrix_wall.03=May be mixed with Assembler Matrix Glass on faces.
tooltip.ae2additions.assembler_matrix_glass.01=Transparent outer wall for Assembler Matrices.
tooltip.ae2additions.assembler_matrix_glass.02=Fills each face of the frame.
tooltip.ae2additions.assembler_matrix_glass.03=May be mixed with Assembler Matrix Wall on faces.
tooltip.ae2additions.assembler_matrix_pattern.01=Install at least 1.
tooltip.ae2additions.assembler_matrix_pattern.02=Each core provides 36 crafting pattern slots.
tooltip.ae2additions.assembler_matrix_pattern.03=Must be placed inside the Assembler Matrix.
tooltip.ae2additions.assembler_matrix_crafter.01=Install at least 1.
tooltip.ae2additions.assembler_matrix_crafter.02=Each core runs 8 crafting jobs at the same time.
tooltip.ae2additions.assembler_matrix_crafter.03=Each core has a fixed drain of 1 AE/t.
tooltip.ae2additions.assembler_matrix_speed.01=Speeds up Assembler Matrix crafting.
